  <brief_title>Effectiveness of Bupivacaine After Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness for Postoperative Pain After Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy of 0,5% Bupivacaine-Soaked Tabotamp Placed in the Gallbladder Bed</official_title>
