  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate the efficacy on postoperative pain of the positioning of a 0,5% bupivacaine
      soaked-tabotamp in gallbladder bed after videolaparoscopic cholecystectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
