  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age&gt;18 years old, ASA 1 and 2

          -  Gallbladder adenomatous polyposis and cholelithiasis with no byochemical, clinical and
             instrumental evidence of acute cholecystitis at the moment of surgery.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age&lt;18 years old

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Previous major surgery of the supramesocholic compartment

          -  Acute cholecystitis

          -  Choledocolitiasis

          -  Acute pancreatitis at the moment of surgery

          -  Laparotomic conversion during surgery
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
